            <div class="opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper ">

                    <span class="opener__topics ">
            <a class="opener__topics-link " href="https://www.propublica.org/topics/immigration">Immigration</a>
        </span>
    
    <h1 class="opener__hed " >        What’s Next for U.S. Immigration Policy on the Southern Border?
    </h1>

    <h2 class="opener__dek " >        ProPublica and The Texas Tribune talked with experts about U.S. border policies that contributed to a deadly detention center fire in Ciudad Juárez, Mexico, and why immigration has become a leading concern in a presidential election year.
    </h2>

    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
