    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/the-right-way-from-venezuela-to-juarez-and-new-york-to-denver-one-familys-asylum-journey">
                                    The Long Journey to Asylum for One Venezuelan Family
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            The Pabón family is among the nearly 8 million Venezuelans who have fled their country. Follow them as they begin a life in the U.S. and journey through an asylum system buckling under record numbers of new arrivals.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/gerardo-del-valle">Gerardo del Valle</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-05-02EDT06:00">May 2, 5 a.m. CDT</time>
