            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/sharon-lerner">Sharon Lerner</a>, photography by <span class="name">Haruka Sakaguchi</span>, special to <a href="https://www.propublica.org">ProPublica</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-05-20EDT06:00">May 20, 6 a.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
                            </div>
                    <div class="most-read-story">
                                    


        
                    
<div class="story-card story-card--standard">
    
    
